re\": 0.9995726167051837, \"rank\": 0.0002943885214075684, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.4178073960078827e-12, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8044713997892726, \"rank\": 0.23947615334624692, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"thesportaftershe\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"any more competitions\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, also known as \\\"B-girl Raygun\\\",went viral on the internetalmost overnight in August after sheperformed unusual movesat the 2024 ParisOlympics, includinga kangaroo hop and a wriggle on the floor.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8044713997892726, \"rank\": 0.23947615334624692, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"B-girl Raygun\\\",went\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"the internetalmost\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 677}, {\"ngram\": \"unusual movesat\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 ParisOlympics\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"includinga kangaroo hop\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"a wriggle\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview last week, she said the scrutiny and backlash over her performance at the Olympics resulted in her wanting to retire.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"the scrutiny\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just did not have any control over how people saw me or who I was.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any control\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was going to keep competing, for sure, but that seems really difficult for me to do now,\\\" she told local radio station2DayFM.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local radio station2DayFM\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the level of scrutiny that's going to be there, and people will be filming it, and it will go online.\\\"\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still break but that's like, in my living room with my partner,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my living room\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"my partner\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in a new interview, she has now said she is not retiring and that her comments were taken out of context.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new interview\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"her comments\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a decision that I did come to, this turned into a story.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I wastalking, you know, on2dayFMabout how I am not going to do certain competitions anymore, which did not seem like such a big deal becausebreakingis not going to be in the Olympics any way,\\\" she saidon theTodayshowon Monday.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain competitions\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"such a big deal\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But you know, I am still going to be part of community jams, or I'd like to go to community jams and still dance and still break.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"community jams\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"community jams\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I never used the word retire - I am not retiring.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the word retire\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You try and stop me, I am not ever going to stop dancing so if you hear that again, you know that it's not the truth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the truth\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said breaking was a \\\"lifestyle\\\" and \\\"you can not retire from culture\\\".\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"lifestyle\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You can not retire from an art form.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an art form\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that's why I am never going to stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old university lecturer from Sydney lost all three of her round-robin contests at the Olympics by a combined score of 54-0 and was ridiculed for her moves on social media.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999960037896739, \"rank\": 3.5487264723135783e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 37-year-old university lecturer\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"her round-robin contests\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"a combined score\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"her moves\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn's performance led to a petition that called for an apology from the athlete as well as Australia's Olympic chef de mission Anna Meares.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8044713997892726, \"rank\": 0.23947615334624692, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\"